# Custom Maps Directory

Place your .pk3 map files here.

Example:
- custom_map_1.pk3
- custom_map_2.pk3
- awesome_arena.pk3

These maps will be:
1. Served via HTTP by the nginx container at http://domain:8080/maps/
2. Mounted into the Xonotic server container at /opt/xonotic/data/
3. Auto-downloaded by clients via sv_curl_defaulturl
